  "translations": {
    "en": "He said: Abul Hasan Ali ibn Bilal al-Mahlabi reported to me from Ali ibn Abdullah al-Isfahani, who reported from Ibrahim ibn Muhammad al-Thaqafi, who reported from Yusuf ibn Sa'id al-Arhabi, who reported from Ubaidullah ibn Musa al-Absi, from Kamil, from Habib ibn Abi Thabit, who said:",
